#!F-adobe-helvetica-medium-r-normal--18*
#!N 
#!CDarkGreen #!N  #!Rtstapi Selecting tools and placing icons #!N #!EC #!N 
#!I0 #!N  #!F-adobe-times-medium-r-normal--18*   #!N #!N #!I30 #!N 1. Click on a 
tool category (e.g.,  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Transformation #!EF ) in the upper palette. 
The tools in that category are now listed in the lower 
palette. #!N #!I30 #!N 2. Click on a tool in the 
lower palette (e.g.,  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   AutoColor #!EF ) to highlight it. #!N 
#!I30 #!N 3. Move the cursor into the canvas area. Note 
that it becomes an inverted "L." #!N #!I30 #!N 4. Position 
the cursor at the point where you want the tool icon 
to appear and click again to generate the icon. #!N #!I0 
